  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3775860/extras/5ee95f85874f46ccabb64c58c85550e3.poster.avif?t=1773759600\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3775860/extras/5ee95f85874f46ccabb64c58c85550e3.webm?t=1773759600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Time to Wizard</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become an all-powerful Wizard in this turn-based party game! Craft unique spells from elemental cards and battle against up to 3 other wizards. Master deep elemental synergies for strategic destruction or embrace wild magic for over-the-top chaos. Fast-paced duels and the luck of the draw ensure no two battles are ever alike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3775860/extras/71e06dd9c3c97330f47a9995f7df88f1.poster.avif?t=1773759600\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3775860/extras/71e06dd9c3c97330f47a9995f7df88f1.webm?t=1773759600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to Play</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each round you will be dealt a hand of elemental cards. You will have a short period of time to select three elements with which to craft your spell.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each element has a basic effect based on where you place it, but if there is a <strong>Wild </strong>element in the primary position, you cast a <strong>Wild Spell</strong> that will have crazy and game shattering effects. Just beware your <strong>Wild Spell</strong> doesn't annihilate you as well...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The last Wizard standing is the winner.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3775860/extras/2be3117afb4e9cac1085b6d0b7d3b3b1.poster.avif?t=1773759600\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3775860/extras/2be3117afb4e9cac1085b6d0b7d3b3b1.webm?t=1773759600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Why you'll love Wild Wizard War</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging multiplayer online experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast paced and engaging battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple gameplay loop with a high skill ceiling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play against friends, strangers or AI bent on your destruction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new Wizard towers to show off your status</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 different Wizards to choose from</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 unique biomes that change your playstyle</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3775860/extras/5ee95f85874f46ccabb64c58c85550e3.poster.avif?t=1773759600\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3775860/extras/5ee95f85874f46ccabb64c58c85550e3.webm?t=1773759600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Time to Wizard</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become an all-powerful Wizard in this turn-based party game! Craft unique spells from elemental cards and battle against up to 3 other wizards. Master deep elemental synergies for strategic destruction or embrace wild magic for over-the-top chaos. Fast-paced duels and the luck of the draw ensure no two battles are ever alike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3775860/extras/71e06dd9c3c97330f47a9995f7df88f1.poster.avif?t=1773759600\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3775860/extras/71e06dd9c3c97330f47a9995f7df88f1.webm?t=1773759600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to Play</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each round you will be dealt a hand of elemental cards. You will have a short period of time to select three elements with which to craft your spell.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each element has a basic effect based on where you place it, but if there is a <strong>Wild </strong>element in the primary position, you cast a <strong>Wild Spell</strong> that will have crazy and game shattering effects. Just beware your <strong>Wild Spell</strong> doesn't annihilate you as well...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The last Wizard standing is the winner.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3775860/extras/2be3117afb4e9cac1085b6d0b7d3b3b1.poster.avif?t=1773759600\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3775860/extras/2be3117afb4e9cac1085b6d0b7d3b3b1.webm?t=1773759600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Why you'll love Wild Wizard War</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging multiplayer online experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast paced and engaging battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple gameplay loop with a high skill ceiling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play against friends, strangers or AI bent on your destruction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new Wizard towers to show off your status</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 different Wizards to choose from</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 unique biomes that change your playstyle</p></li></ul>",
