      "review_text": "This game was fun to learn. Actually some cool mechanics going on and unique spells. I feel if this game were fleshed out more it would be a pretty dope party game. It becomes a bit less fun when you learn all the chaos spell combos. I feel as though there should be more randomization built into spells in some way.",
